    "bio_summary": "Rema (birth name Divine Ikubor)  is a Nigerian afrobeat and hip-hop artist from Benin City, Edo State. His critically acclaimed EPs have changed the wave of hip-hop/trap in Nigeria, with the songs \"Iron Man\" and \"Spiderman\" were featured on Obama's music list in 2019, while \"Dumebi\" was a global hit. His debut album Rave & Roses was released on March 25, 2022. <a href=\"https://www.last.fm/music/Rema\">Read more on Last.fm</a>",
